w you will be asked to complete stanford's employment application form about working at stanford in addition to providing current job listings the stanford jobs website is an excellent source of information about working at stanford including details about employee benefits and perks it is the policy of stanford university to comply with all applicable affirmative action requirements in accordance with law it is also the university's policy to provide equal employment opportunities for all applicants and employees in compliance with applicable laws office contacts directors jennifer trimble director of human resources jleavitt stanford edu 650 723.3574 jaime alburger human resources administrator jalburger law stanford edu 650 725.9539 angela arroyo associate director human resources aarroyo stanford edu 650 725.7020 recorded & past events may 2007 wellness fair may 9 2007 from 10 00 am 3 00 pm contact information stanford law school office of human resources crown quadrangle 559 nathan abbott way stanford ca 94305 8610 human resources law stanford edu resources benefitsu jobs stanford university human resources department related links 2011 all hands presentation employee engagement survey results 2011 all hands presentation professional development working group recommendations & feedback needed 2011 all hands presentation communications working group survey results recommendations and feedback needed cloudy 51 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
